Interface com.chimu.form.mapping.MappedObject

public interface MappedObject
The MappedObject interface is used to determine whether a particular object is a FORM mapped object or not, and to provide the protocol for interacting with that object. Any object that is used with an ObjectMapper must support this protocol.

See Also:
